## 2. 評估紀錄 (Pre-anesthetic Assessment)
*此部分勾選後，主項會對應 PDF 左側 Yes/No 框，細項則串接顯示於筆記區。*

### A. 心血管系統 (Cardiovascular System)
- **(1) Hypertension (高血壓)**: `chk_cv_htn`, `chk_cv_htn_reg`, `chk_cv_htn_poor`
- **(2) CAD (冠狀動脈疾病)**: `chk_cv_cad`, `chk_cv_cad_poba`, `chk_cv_cad_cabg`, `chk_cv_cad_oth`, `txt_cv_cad_oth`
- **(3) Valvular disease**: `chk_cv_valve`, `txt_cv_valve_note`
- **(4) Arrhythmia (心律不整)**: `chk_cv_arr`, `chk_cv_arr_pm`, `chk_cv_arr_af` (Paroxysmal/Persistent), `chk_cv_arr_avb` (1/M1/M2/Complete), `chk_cv_arr_stt`, `chk_cv_arr_abl`, `chk_cv_arr_oth`, `txt_cv_arr_oth_note`
- **(5) Heart failure (心衰竭)**: `chk_cv_hf`, `sel_cv_hf_nyha`, `chk_cv_hf_pef`, `chk_cv_hf_ref`
- (6) Dyslipidemia: `chk_cv_lipid`, `chk_cv_lipid_med`
- (7) PAOD: `chk_cv_paod`
- (8) Vascular disease: `chk_cv_vasc`, `chk_cv_vasc_aneur`, `chk_cv_vasc_diss`, `chk_cv_vasc_oth`, `txt_cv_vasc_oth`
- (9) Congenital Heart Disease: `chk_cv_congen`
- (10) Pulmonary Hypertension: `chk_cv_ph`
- (11) Others: `chk_cv_oth`, `txt_cv_oth`

### B. 神經精神系統 (Neurologic & Psychiatric)
- (1) CVA: `chk_neu_cva` (Ischemic/Hemorrhagic/Hemiparesis R&L), `chk_neu_cva_oth`, `txt_neu_cva_oth`
- (2) TBI: `chk_neu_tbi`
- (3) Parkinson: `chk_neu_park`
- (4) Seizure: `chk_neu_seiz`, `chk_neu_seiz_reg`
- (5) Aneurysm/AVM: `chk_neu_avm`, `chk_neu_avm_med`, `chk_neu_avm_surg`
- (6) Dementia: `chk_neu_dem`
- (7) Psychiatric Problem: `chk_neu_psych` (Schiz/Bipolar/Depression/Personality), `chk_neu_psych_oth`, `txt_neu_psych_oth`
- (8) GCS: `chk_neu_gcs`, `sel_neu_gcs_e`, `sel_neu_gcs_v`, `sel_neu_gcs_m`
- (9) Cerebral Palsy: `chk_neu_cp`
- (10) Others: `chk_neu_oth`, `txt_neu_oth`

### C. 內分泌系統 (Endocrine System)
- (1) DM: `chk_end_dm`, `chk_end_dm_oad`, `chk_end_dm_ins`, `chk_end_dm_oth`, `txt_end_dm_oth`
